{"title":"回答——给喀麦隆同志","authors":["达尔玛瓦第"],"dates":[{"year":1964,"month":2,"day":27}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"回答"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——给喀麦隆同志"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔印度尼西亚〕达尔玛瓦第"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你来到我这里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"问起："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要和平还是要独立？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我毫不犹豫地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"回答你：要独立！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尽管为了它，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"死亡在等着。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我懂得你的爱呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但我没有别的选择！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我说："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不可能，世界会和平，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而我这块土地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却是监狱和饥馑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对我来说，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有这个选择："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"举枪反抗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还是举手投降？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我选择举枪反抗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了挣脱一切捆绑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我懂得你的爱呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但我没有别的选择！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"与其为和平受屈辱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不如为独立抛头颅！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔居三元译〕"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}